tags.description: The Fly’n B House, formerly known as the Plews House, was built by Matthew Plews in 1906. Mr. Plews was a talented horticulturalist who ran a truck garden on the property for many years. Fly’n B Park was built and opened in 2010. Many apple trees here.
tags.name: Fly’n B Park
